						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Fragment of a stone lying in the village Chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p>13th-14th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">13th-14th Century A.D.,</hi> seems to register a gift of land and house-site by the <hi rend="italic">mūligas</hi> and several persons to god Svayaṁbhudēva.</p>						

						</summary>
